(11, 'tut1', 'Equipment intro / outro Desktop ,labtop or tablet', 0, 'backend', '<p><span>To become a successful in this business, you need the right tools. The most important tool is&nbsp;</span><strong>you</strong><span>, since&nbsp;</span><strong>you</strong><span>&nbsp;are the product people are paying to see. Therefore, you should do everything possible to maintain the best possible attitude and appearance for your custoers. Believe it or not, being a successful webcam model has very little to do with the content of your shows. I found that technology, reliability, and attitude are the real keys to success. Perfect all three, and you will be ahead of the game.</span></p>\r\n<p><span><span>The remaining tools you will need are:</span><img src="http://camclients.com/beta/images/rocketlauncher/frontpage/roksprocket-tabs/Computer-and-laptop.png" alt="" border="0" /><span class="image-description">Features include an intuitive administrative interface</span></span></p>\r\n<h3 class="largemargintop nomarginbottom">Desktop or Labtop</h3>\r\n<p>There is no single brand of computer All you really need is a computer with a lot of memory, and preferably a fast processor. We recommend that you are running a minimum of Windows 98 or Mac OS with at least 1GB of ram.</p>\r\n<p><span><span class="image-description">&nbsp;</span></span></p>\r\n<p><span><span class="image-description">&nbsp;</span></span></p>\r\n<p>Please&nbsp;<a href="http://www.camjobs4models.com/contact">contact us</a>&nbsp;if you have any questions about equipment or your Internet connection. If you have any concerns about any of the equipment you''re buying, feel free to call us while you''re at the store. We are here to help you become successful, so don''t hesitate to ask for help if you need it.</p>\r\n<p>You can run our software on any connection speed, but we suggest using a faster connection to increase the quality of your video stream.</p>\r\n<p><span><span class="image-description">&nbsp;</span></sp